  backstory: "My name is Ati-Purusa, a lightfoot halfling born under the whispering leaves of the forests. From an early age, I learned the art of subtlety and deception, blending seamlessly into my surroundings like a whisper in the wind. My chaotic-good alignment stems from my belief in doing what's right, even if it means bending a few rules along the way.\n\nCalmness is my virtue, never allowing the chaos of the world to ruffle my feathers. I speak softly, if at all, and my voice never raises above a hushed tone. In any situation, I always have a plan, and another, and yet another waiting in the wings, ready to be executed should the need arise. Flexibility is the key to survival, and I am a master of adaptation.\n\nMy mastery of disguise is my most potent weapon, allowing me to slip past even the keenest eyes unnoticed. Loyalty is a rare currency in my world, but to those I call friends, it is a treasure beyond measure. I care little for lofty ideals or grand causes; my loyalty lies with the people I trust, and the rest can fend for themselves.\n\nBut there is a burning ember within me, fueled by the injustice of a stolen treasure. Something dear was taken from me, and I aim to reclaim it, by any means necessary. Even if it means allowing an innocent soul to take the fall for a crime I committed, for in the grand scheme of things, sacrifices must be made.\n\nIn my pursuit, I am aided by a reliable and trustworthy contact, a liaison to a network of fellow criminals. Through them, I navigate the shadowy underworld with ease, sending and receiving messages over great distances through the web of corrupt messengers, caravan masters, and seafaring sailors.\n\nSleight of hand, deception, and the deft use of thieves' tools are my trades, honed through years of practice and refinement. With these skills at my disposal, I move through the world like a ghost, leaving behind only whispers and rumors in my wake.",
